node.text: Divine timing! It was just released today , 1 day shy of being a week #postpartum . This week has not been what I expected, it’s hard work and a lot of adjusting right now and emotional rollercoaster. I needed this reminder ! Thank you @roxylook @blackbeltbeauty for allowing me to chat with you and be my authentic self. Link to the full show is in my bio and stories . ❤️ Sending you love and light . ✨

node.text: These pregnancy pains are no joke! Especially now in the #thirdtrimester ! I filmed this at 6 months, I’m now 8 months and way bigger and feeling even more pain ! These tips really help ! If you’re preggo ask your physician before trying of course. If you’re not, watch and enjoy me looking/feeling like humpty dumpy! 🤰🏽😅#preggoprobs #preggostretches #happypreggo #healthypregnancy
